This paper deals with natural language processing (NLP) and machine learning techniques to analyze privacy policies. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CL (Computation and Language). The paper also deals with privacy and security, which suggests that it could belong to cs.CR (Cryptography and Security). The use of machine learning techniques suggests that it could belong to cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.LG (Machine Learning). Finally, the paper deals with information retrieval, which suggests that it could belong to cs.IR (Information Retrieval).
